segmentosSRT.text: Careful, slowly. Don't move too fast!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
Your mother's not well.
Go now, for her sake.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I'll look after her for a few days?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
- On one of the wounded.
- It's a killing field.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Said he was a saboteur. I had to.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Youqing's not going to any stupid show.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: and blinds all who look within
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I yell there's no time to waste
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Far away, we flee with haste
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
I just caught them on a ladder,
pulling off roof tiles.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: No idea! The leader is a cripple.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Clear a path! Ship sailing through!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
The ship of revolution! Advance
through the storm with Chairman Mao!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12
